{"tid":1218654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱坐鐵 聽到兩個中坑傾計","createTime":"2019-06-13T16:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T11:05:40.000Z","uid":144187,"like":97,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2c60622695ac233ca2926b675e577c5ea197350f","tid":1218654,"uid":144187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:24:55.000Z","msg":"兩個人都係中年，望落去黑黑實實，似係地盤佬。本身佢地傾緊啲示威者點樣暴力，跟住其中一個話自己個仔都有上前線。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重點</span></span><strong></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n其中一個突然解釋俾另外條友聽，送中條例有咩問題，仲要引返書店件事，話俾佢聽過咗就可以合法捉人返去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲一定冇可能係佢地自己諗到，一定係仔女講返件事俾佢聽先會噏得出！！<br />\n<br />\n證明 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣 係好撚有用架！！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">文宣 係好撚有用架！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣 係好撚有用架！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c44ba6c3b723fd6ff7747ae55091d7900521634c","tid":1218654,"uid":149844,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:47:45.000Z","msg":"呼籲各大市民即日開始行街見到警犬就噓佢<br />\n屌多兩句老母都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n強烈遣責警方使用過大武力打市民,記者,各宗教人士,老師等等<br />\n用口水屌死班差佬 市民睇到啲報道點諗唔重要 但班警犬咁打人真係好過份<br />\n<br />\n各位市民依幾日可以自由參與各種宗教活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期日一定要上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e101ebcc99c1cb1aa2709a73f16ebd47c580501","tid":1218654,"uid":144187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:16:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ba6fa39f16f7bcabccc517d0f38a098fe6111b5","tid":1218654,"uid":144187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"